		<title>Fusion BPO Brings Win-Win Quality Assurance with 5 Basic Strategies</title>
		<link>https://www.fusionbposervices.com/blog/fusion-bpo-brings-win-win-quality-assurance-with-5-basic-strategies.html</link>
				<comments>https://www.fusionbposervices.com/blog/fusion-bpo-brings-win-win-quality-assurance-with-5-basic-strategies.html#respond</comments>
				<pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2013 12:59:30 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Alicia Johnson]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Call Center]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Quality Assurance]]></category>
